::DarkMouse::

She saw the shields go up and stood back in self dissappointment.
Not only had she not fully accomplished her mission, but she left 
Quickstrike behind.  She sat next to the now shielded hatch and 
looked at the situation.  She could hear Megatron talking to some 
ohter bot on the other side of the ship. megatron's voice carried 
well.
So she had a choice, she could tell Megatron to try to talk to them 
about releasing Quickstrike.  Or she could try to attempt to break in 
and save him on her own. She thought for a moment.  She could do both.

She ran around the ship until Megatron came into view.  She walked 
calmly over to megatron and whispered to him, "They have Quickstrike 
prisoner in the ship.  See if they will release him."  She then spoke 
in a louder voice so she knew she would be heard,"I will return to 
the base Commander. I need to use the CR chamber and then I shall 
return to your side. Oh great Commander Megatron." She curtsied, 
turned and walked away like she was heading for her base. 

She walked through the trees, doubled back and went back to the hatch 
way.  She thought, if there was one hatch, surely there must be 
another somewhere.  She started her recon around looking for another 
way in.
